-DATASET CSV EMPTY

--

-CASE TestListToString

-STATEMENT return list_to_string(NULL, NULL)
---- error
Runtime exception: Trying to a create a vector with ANY type. This should not happen. Data type is expected to be resolved during binding.

-STATEMENT return list_to_string(NULL, [5, 6, 7, 8])
---- 1

-STATEMENT return list_to_string(NULL, ['5', '6', '7', '8'])
---- 1

-STATEMENT return list_to_string(list_to_string('', []), ['helloworld'])
---- 1
helloworld

-STATEMENT return list_to_string('', [])
---- 1

